<p>
	<b>Suggested Criteria:</b><br>
	1. Purpose - The reason you want to meet this person.<br>
	2. Location - Where you want this person or thing to be located.<br>
	3. Time - When you want this person or thing to be available.<br>
	4. Goal - The objective you would like to meet.<br>
	5. Interests - What interests you want to connect on.<br>
	6. Condition - What conditions should be met.<br>
	8. Qualification - What you have to offer.<br>
	9. Personality - What your personality is like.<br>
	10. Additional Information - Anything else that's relevant.<br>
